  "time_ut": 1661334321,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd8\u0dc2\u0dd2 \u0d87\u0db8\u0dad\u0dd2  \u0d9b\u0db1\u0dd2\u0da2 \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0d82\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0db4\u0daf\u0dd2\u0d82\u0da0\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dd6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Minister of Agriculture is preparing to move to the Petroleum Corporation",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Agriculture, Wildlife and Forest Resources, Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera said that if he does not get the necessary fuel for agriculture, he will have to go to the Petroleum Corporation and settle there until he gets the fuel.",
        "The Minister of Agriculture also said that the problem of obtaining fuel for the agriculture industry will be resolved by going to the Petroleum Corporation and settling there.",
        "The Minister of Agriculture said this in a discussion held with the district representatives of the National Agricultural Union on the cultivation activities of the upcoming season.",
        "The Minister of Agriculture also mentioned that private companies have focused on a program to sell insecticides, herbicides and fungicides through agricultural centers."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Petroleum Corporation",
